            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَهُوَ فِی عِیشَةࣲ رَّاضِیَةࣲ ۝٢١﴾ مرضية</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "69:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فِی جَنَّةٍ عَالِیَةࣲ ۝٢٢﴾</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "69:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿قُطُوفُهَا﴾ ثِمَارهَا ﴿دَانِیَةࣱ ۝٢٣﴾ قَرِيبَة يَتَنَاوَلهَا الْقَائِم وَالْقَاعِد والمضطجع</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "69:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>فَيُقَال لَهُمْ ﴿كُلُوا۟ وَٱشۡرَبُوا۟ هَنِیۤـَٔۢا﴾ حَال أَيْ مُتَهَنِّئِينَ ﴿بِمَاۤ أَسۡلَفۡتُمۡ فِی ٱلۡأَیَّامِ ٱلۡخَالِیَةِ ۝٢٤﴾ الْمَاضِيَة في الدنيا</p>"
        },
        "25": {
